To biro cʉ̃ ca ĩiro jiro cʉ̃ buerã waari, bojocare: “Tʉgoeña yeri wajoa, Ʉmʉreco Pacʉre tʉo nʉnʉjeeya,” cʉ̃jare ĩi wede majio,
