To biro cʉ̃ ca ĩiro, Jesús pea cʉ̃ capere ñia peo nemoupi ñucã. To biro cʉ̃ ca tiiro, ñee jãa maniro añuro ĩa, diarique manigʉpʉ tuacãupi yua.
Cʉ̃ ca wederijere, “To biirije yʉ ĩicu,” ĩi majiticãupi, niipetirãpʉra ʉcʉa yaicoama ĩirã.
To cõrora wãtĩ pea bʉaro acaro bui, ñañaropʉ cʉ̃re tii wẽe yaye cõa cũu cojo, witicoaupi. Cʉ̃ pea ca dia waaricʉre biropʉ biicã cũmu waaupi. To biri paʉ, “Dia yaicoami,” ĩiupa.
