Jãa majuropeera ate wederique ʉmʉreco tutipʉ ca doorijere, cʉ̃ mena ʉ̃tãgʉ ca añuricʉ jotoapʉ niirã jãa tʉowʉ.
Cʉ̃ja, mee tĩrʉmʉpʉra Ʉmʉreco Pacʉ cʉ̃ ca wederora ati ʉmʉreco, ati yepa, cãa nii, oco watoa ca niiriquerena tii bau nii, ocora ca tuu ñeero tii, cʉ̃ ca tiiriquere,
To ca bii pacaro, cʉ̃ ca dotirore biro ca tii nʉnʉjeegʉ pea, díámacʉ̃ra Ʉmʉreco Pacʉre maigʉ tiimi. O biri wãme mani ca biirije mena, Ʉmʉreco Pacʉ yaarã mani ca niirijere mani maji.
To biri Jesucristo mena to birora ca niicõa niirã, ñañarijere tiitima. Ñañarijere ca tiirã niipetirãpʉra Jesucristore ĩati, cʉ̃re majiti, ca biiricarã niima.
Jĩcʉ̃ ʉnora jĩcãti ʉno peera Ʉmʉreco Pacʉre ĩatiupa. Mani ca maijata, mani menara niimi Ʉmʉreco Pacʉ. Ñucã manire cʉ̃ ca mairije cãa, ĩa majiricarora manire bii nʉnʉa waa.
Yʉ punaa, tii nʉcʉ̃ bʉoricarã ca bii ditorã menare bojoca catiri niiña.
Yoari méé yʉ waarucu biigʉpʉa. To cõropʉ añuro mʉ mena mani wede penijaco.
Ate nii, Jesucristo, cʉ̃re ca pade bojarãre, yoari mééra ca biipere cʉ̃ ĩñojato ĩigʉ, Ʉmʉreco Pacʉ cʉ̃re cʉ̃ ca ĩñorique. Jesucristo, yʉ cʉ̃re pade bojari majʉ Juan're ate cʉ̃ ca ĩariquere yʉ ca majipere biro ĩigʉ, cʉ̃ yʉʉ queti wederi majʉ  mena wede doti cojoupi.
Ca Catigʉ yʉ nii. Yʉ bii yaicoawʉ ména. Ca bii yaicoaricʉ nii pacagʉ, mecʉ̃ra to birora ca caticõa niigʉ yʉ nii. Yʉa, bii yairiquere, ñucã to birora ñañaro ca bii yairã cʉ̃ja ca niiropʉ cãare,  doti majiriquere yʉ cʉo.
